<p>We accept both <a href="/user/deposit/bitcoin">Bitcoins</a> and <a href="/user/deposit/namecoin">Namecoins</a> as deposit option. If you want to know more - 
checkout <a href='http://www.bitcoin.org' target='_blank'>http://www.dot-bit.org</a></p>

<p>It must be noted that Moonco.in is not an exchange, depositing NMC will only allow you to play on Name-Mooncoin tables. Whereas depositing BTC will only allow you to play on Bit-Mooncoin tables.</p>

<h2>Namecoin Deposit</h2>

<p>We have generated address for all your transactions. Any money sent to this 
address will be deposited to your account. Please note, that we wait until we 
get at least one confirmation of the transaction, so it will take some time for 
sent namecoins to appear here. This delay depends on network size and load at 
this moment.</p>
<div style="border: solid 1px; padding-left: 10px;padding-right:10px; width: 500px;">
<p><strong>You need to come back to this page when you will see confirmations of your
transaction in order to finalize depositing of namecoins.</strong></p>

<p>Namecoin address: <strong>[% namecoin_address %]</strong></p>

<p>Current exchange rate: 1 NMC = 100 Mooncoins(Chips).</p>

<p>You sent so far <strong>&#xe3f;[% namecoins_sent | format('%.2f') %]</strong>.</p>
